				<p>About Us : </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-12  aboutInfo ">
				<p>We have Aadhar card, Pan card, Voter id, driving license like
					identity proofs for our day to day transactions. But we
					have major missing that is our health card, which manages our day
					to day health history like disease, allergy etc. <br>
					<hr>
					The main problem in today's date is we are not having any centralize
					database of individual person, and because of that it is impossible to take proper
					precaution for prevention of any viral disease. <br>
					<hr>
					Next is when doctor give any prescription to patient doctor do not have
					any record of that prescription. So next time if doctor wants
					to take any past reference of same patient than it is not possible. <br>
					<hr>
					We are creating a centralize database of every patient’s medical history in an online system where
					we
					can store medical history of patient’s. <br>
					<hr>
					In that system every individual patient’s should have a unique ID or Health Card
					number through which all medical activities can be stored online.<br>
					<hr>
					In that system only authorised doctors can update the
					patient’s treatment from the database which in
					future can be referred.
				</p>
			</div>
